  "prompt": "Where can I see a Lamborghini in Bangalore?",
  "response": "In Bangalore, there are several places where you might see a Lamborghini:\n\n1. **Lamborghini Showroom**: The official Lamborghini dealership in Bangalore, located on Vittal Mallya Road, often has a variety of models on display. Visiting the showroom is a great way to see a range of Lamborghinis up close.\n\n2. **Luxury Car Events and Auto Shows**: Bangalore frequently hosts automotive events and luxury car shows. Keep an eye out for events like the Bangalore International Automotive Expo or specific luxury car showcases.\n\n3. **High-End Areas**: You might spot a Lamborghini on the roads in upscale neighborhoods such as Koramangala, Indiranagar, or Whitefield. These areas are known for affluent residents who might own luxury vehicles.\n\n4. **Luxury Hotels**: High-end hotels like The Ritz-Carlton or The Leela Palace often have luxury cars parked outside, either belonging to guests or being displayed as part of promotional events.\n\n5. **Car Meets and Clubs**: Bangalore has several car enthusiast groups and clubs that organize meetups and drives. Groups like the Bangalore Exotic Car Club often gather and showcase exotic cars, including Lamborghinis.\n\nChecking out these locations and events will give you a great chance of seeing a Lamborghini in Bangalore.",
